# SnapPrint – Swift Package Dependencies
# Star Micronics no longer supports CocoaPods (deprecated as of StarIO V2.12.3+)
# SDK is now distributed via Swift Package Manager.
#
# HOW TO ADD VIA XCODE (preferred):
#   1. Open SnapPrint.xcodeproj in Xcode
#   2. File → Add Package Dependencies...
#   3. Add each URL below:
#
#   StarIO (core port communication):
#     https://github.com/star-micronics/stario-ios
#
#   StarIO_Extension (command builder for images, text, cut):
#     https://github.com/star-micronics/stario-extension-ios
#
# Both packages → add to target "SnapPrint"
#
# After adding, uncomment the StarIO SDK calls in:
#   SnapPrint/Services/PrinterService.swift
